gov.usgs.anss.picker

Interface PickerCallback


  • public interface PickerCallback
    This is the interface that the CWBPicker (or any later supplier of data to a picker) uses. It allow the pickers themselves to be free of code related to reporting picks, saving state, making files, etc.
